  <Document>
    <name>The St Michael Line in UK</name>
    <description>Map showing the two currents (Michael and Mary) plotted in detail across the UK. The map has four layers: The Michael alignment (Blue), The Mary current (Green) and The Michael current (Red) and markers layer with links to paintings.</description>
