      <Placemark>
        <name>St Michael, Othery</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5qDtjBiRiNe4uURy-jBsMa6TyVJ5M2q-vvpOXQzPekRrUnNWjXWN1YauwTetzcx9sXnSMk0LAKY0nzvmxiTTpD7Y8lltUSHMcr7KhOF9LV5ctXVlLPg58P0H8K0A" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>St Michael thrusts his spear in to the mouth of the writhing dragon over the door of Othery Church. Inside a similar image on tiles except the dragon has a human head]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-503-DB4436-labelson</styleUrl>
