      <Placemark>
        <name>Dorchester Big Rings Henge</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7lMEj-Dc8torWRenX9ZTDVCCC1SgJfg1SQAiPlEZpXZpoApNnIU4pis36Nne856RaAhx1DjBqJqREzoOromdSu0QzAwFTazoTHzVDe6j6wCH2xWSohsVjdaaM" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>The Henge monument to the north of Dorchester, known locally as the "big rings", was sadly lost to aggregate extraction in the 1970s.]]></description>
