      <Placemark>
        <name>Avebury</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v43FFO2O__yCF9p5QcFQ3gPRq3g8ONbjQPa1ZkvzDI4dyqWimEJ3pGTpgG68Cph6Jdu8O78jxRN4C1bDs4yVP2_izsI_0XHfwazyE10c_Y38uEecA" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This big stone is The Devil's Chair. The largest of the Avebury megaliths left today. The pair of stones mark the southern entrance to the henge and a second node of both currents after having passed through the node point near the chapel. A concrete plinth near the chapel now marks where the tallest stone, a  30 foot high by 8 foot thick Obelisk, that was recorded in 1747 by William Stukeley. The other images show how Avebury was part of a whole 'sacred' landscape and the henge here is linked along the currents to the Sanctuary, Windmill Hill and Knoll Down. <br><br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4LqtxI7b9mJ3xglJYOiUs1TGNMX4e0rbdSsBlQuuzJhPLt_DqY9V8b1_licwkGRGvyWS7Aby5HMIu6_awg7A3hhmYu23u2mfMobn3jHJrQtDlevTDGtQ" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v56CbuFyYApnT8DHM6tBlk1TiAxKB0pvdBX65n-7TdmZjEB1ctFgZp35Teniss37Mhy2bxFxZuMKJl-ATETGY2Q-vmUUdof6PkTOTHJnSW8y9ewLw3THnteK-xV" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7UHO5jKCNv3_djQJ1u4u9GEd-6gSK2p0svLn9huEwm5DGJI2r3x8EuPULbPGPJo6p5lb1LPvGf-RfeFTd5mOqjJhhlB5fl-1Gc064z" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-503-DB4436-labelson</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v43FFO2O__yCF9p5QcFQ3gPRq3g8ONbjQPa1ZkvzDI4dyqWimEJ3pGTpgG68Cph6Jdu8O78jxRN4C1bDs4yVP2_izsI_0XHfwazyE10c_Y38uEecA https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v4LqtxI7b9mJ3xglJYOiUs1TGNMX4e0rbdSsBlQuuzJhPLt_DqY9V8b1_licwkGRGvyWS7Aby5HMIu6_awg7A3hhmYu23u2mfMobn3jHJrQtDlevTDGtQ https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v56CbuFyYApnT8DHM6tBlk1TiAxKB0pvdBX65n-7TdmZjEB1ctFgZp35Teniss37Mhy2bxFxZuMKJl-ATETGY2Q-vmUUdof6PkTOTHJnSW8y9ewLw3THnteK-xV https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7UHO5jKCNv3_djQJ1u4u9GEd-6gSK2p0svLn9huEwm5DGJI2r3x8EuPULbPGPJo6p5lb1LPvGf-RfeFTd5mOqjJhhlB5fl-1Gc064z</value>
