        <name>St Michaels, Clifden Hampden</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5lrKPj-pCjIjUCc-cQlCBLva13LTlNdxsk3afspUXTS1EzgnJLzdlbOHn95wProLjC5gdZCp9iwwXchdgTv2kbzqDOLsckg0cXrYKluZtIcLjJTN-00kO6Zg" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Carved wooden St Michael glows deep brown in the rood screen. Pillar and mound near church marks current. ]]></description>
