        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6DyuVy09JJMIEWthoVRZwJ7OIGploGymne8o_3J2jgk5lhyu7HibU8jsIEhKOY70-nz9D9WFAAUQDUK-aOvuNkYxlec14MHq1vwKVTQ4PAlHk" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Originally a wooden structure rebuilt by the monks of Glastonbury. Two dragons look down from the walls. ]]></description>
