      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Druid's Cross]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6i3iheE20wgYw9H4mEYvRlSBKGYXYX2LoSad3cfbuxEOLUvIB7-UKtJTQZIqM7Pumr4J4HCcb58wKRDs74LN_DGI1nRuPSJzRrxT1VduAaKOaRuXUrNQ" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>In the woods of Boconnoc Estate.  Druidic ritual centre with 8 tracks leading in to this enchanted Glade with a cross. The inscription on the cross reads: "On this Hill, once the site of Druid Idolatry and in later times the scene of civil bloodshed, This ancient symbol of the holy religion of the redeemer is erected in greater acknowledgement of the blessings of a pure faith and of a peaceful country"]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-503-DB4436-labelson</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6i3iheE20wgYw9H4mEYvRlSBKGYXYX2LoSad3cfbuxEOLUvIB7-UKtJTQZIqM7Pumr4J4HCcb58wKRDs74LN_DGI1nRuPSJzRrxT1VduAaKOaRuXUrNQ</value>
