      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Durston</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v56ys5DWrRxsCzgX5p2HNJhn3OWokU4CGciwowDX6kntL03eADbxd4t3Y20yvwsf_IDNaSwi9fZpPe3U9WSco0xBWCmXlYQ3Tl1Rkq82t0TMy4" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>"..Current runs through tower and porch. the whole place has the feeling of a monastic settlement, with its holy well, duckpond, manor house and carved stones lying about,..."]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-503-DB4436-labelson</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v56ys5DWrRxsCzgX5p2HNJhn3OWokU4CGciwowDX6kntL03eADbxd4t3Y20yvwsf_IDNaSwi9fZpPe3U9WSco0xBWCmXlYQ3Tl1Rkq82t0TMy4</value>
