        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6S5iNSvaJLuvOCPDrXimOkpayXx0GBL82Vpmey7AtUGrmiz9KqH7CujG9ne8ycb88l0KZd7RggJEMLsBSmyWrU2FCR3X5kLswFwKJIZ_--7P-r" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>St Cleer is famous for its holy well and its magical properties.  Mary runs diagonally through the bell tower through an ancient 'eye' stone.]]></description>
